    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it\u2019s in incredible shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and has been pampered since day one. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. This example boasts a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and subframe inspection. Finished in flawless Alpine White over Novillo leather, this vehicle offers a visceral, analog driving experience with zero mechanical compromises and a perfect service pedigree.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Detailed service history. Garage kept. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a true collector-grade specimen that remains in showroom condition. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been meticulously preserved; there are no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found, and the factory wheels are completely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule, featuring supple, unmarked Nappa leather that still retains its original scent. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions with the crisp precision of a new car. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, having been maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. It comes with a complete, chronological service history from authorized specialists, documenting every preventative measure taken since it left the dealership. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in rain or snow, this car is for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
