      "description": "We are pleased to present an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in impeccable condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards of care. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a commitment to excellence. This is a rare acquisition opportunity for the driver who demands uncompromising quality and a showroom-level experience.",
      "price": 48750.0,
