      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready condition\u2014it\u2019s been totally pampered since day one! No scratches, no dents, and it still feels like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s essentially brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
