    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an impeccable E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the S54B32 power plant, showcasing its 8,000 RPM redline through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the rod bearing service is completed, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with OEM-plus bushings. The exterior retains its factory-original luster, while the cabin is free of typical wear. A true driver\u2019s specimen maintained to an exacting standard.",
